OL,6,FThe index is calculated based on
OL,7,Fmonthly surveys from a sample of
OL,8,Fconsumers and measures people's
OL,9,Fopinions on a range of economic
OL,10,Ffactors. These include general
OL,11,Feconomic outlook, household finances,
OL,12,Fsaving intentions and openness to
OL,13,Fspend money on big-ticket items.
OL,15,FDuring times when consumers feel more
OL,16,Ffinancially stable, this naturally
OL,17,Finfluences their spending patterns.
