OL,3,CConsumer confidence rises ahead of
OL,4,CBlack Friday
OL,6,FNovember's improvement was driven by a
OL,7,Fjump in intentions to make major
OL,8,Fpurchases by five points to minus 16,
OL,9,Fwhich shows increased confidence in
OL,10,Fbuying big-ticket items.
OL,12,FWith Black Friday next week and
OL,13,FChristmas not far around the corner,
OL,14,Fthis figure is eight points higher
OL,15,Fthan the same time last year.
OL,17,FConfidence in personal finances for
OL,18,Fthe year ahead rose by one point to
OL,19,Fminus one ` two points higher than
OL,20,Fthis time last year.
