OL,3,CConsumer confidence rises ahead of
OL,4,CBlack Friday
OL,6,FExpectations for the general economic
OL,7,Fsituation are up two points, but
OL,8,Fremain at minus 26.
OL,10,FNeil Bellamy, GfK consumer insights
OL,11,Fdirector, said: "There was evidence of
OL,12,Fnervousness in recent months as
OL,13,Fconsumers contemplated the potentially
OL,14,Fworrying impact of the UK Budget at
OL,15,Fhome and even the implications of the
OL,16,FUS presidential election, but we have
OL,17,Fmoved past those events now."
