OL,6,FHowever, Bellamy warns that it is
OL,7,Fstill "too early to expect significant
OL,8,Ffurther improvements in the consumer
OL,9,Fmood", adding that "people are still
OL,10,Ffeeling acute cost-of-living
OL,11,Fpressures, and it will take time for
OL,12,Fthe UK's new government to deliver on
OL,13,Fits promise of 'change'".
